---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import img from '~/assets/tito_xd-cafe-manager-by-frankuwu.png';
import SplitHero from '~/components/SplitHero.astro';
import { SiteDescription, SiteTitle } from '~/config';
import ScaffoldLayout from '~/layouts/ScaffoldLayout.astro';
---

<ScaffoldLayout title={SiteTitle} description={SiteDescription} currentNav="Home">
	<SplitHero title={`路上辛苦了\n喝点什么？`} className="home-intro">
		<Picture
			slot="art"
			class="home-intro__art"
			src={img}
			formats={['avif', 'webp']}
			alt="Tito_XD original character coffee master version by Frankuwu"
			sizes="(max-width: 767px) 18rem, (max-width: 1023px) 20rem, 21rem"
			loading="eager"
		/>
		<p>我是 Tito_XD，本店的店长，也可以叫我头头。</p>
		<p>不知不觉已经走进春天了，生活又要这样继续往前走了。捡着空闲时间和摸鱼稍稍微装修了一下这里，看到这里不知道有没有觉得有点新意呢。</p>
		<p>总归还是生活碎碎念。如果我的寥寥几字也能让你驻足停看，那也不错，谢谢。</p>
		<p class="home-intro__links">
			<a href="/posts/rewind-2025">2025 年的 REWIND 在这里</a>，
			<a href="/posts/onward-2026">2026 年的 ONWARD 在这里</a>。
		</p>
		<p>欢迎光临，请开心。</p>
	</SplitHero>
</ScaffoldLayout>

<style>
	.home-intro__links {
		color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text) 92%, var(--color-muted));
	}

	.home-intro__links a {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		text-decoration-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 54%, transparent);
		text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
	}

	.home-intro__links a:hover,
	.home-intro__links a:focus-visible {
		color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 84%, var(--color-text));
	}
</style>
